\nquadrupole and octupole and may be related with the low CMB temperature\nvariance anomaly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Nov 2021 19:10:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 09:21:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-14"}
