, the instrument is well\nunderstood, and the first year of data is already yielding useful science\nresults. Experience with this Pathfinder will drive the design of the next\ngenerations of experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Nov 2021 20:45:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2021 06:24:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 22:27:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
