rvey the types of communities for which this approach\nmight be best suited and then review the analytical techniques available for\nquantifying metabolite dynamics in communities. Finally, we discuss what types\nof data analysis approaches might be lucrative for learning the\nstructure-function mapping in communities from these data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 15:39:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-20"}
