ering this way a wide range of operating\nconditions. For these tests, in the former case the counter terminal is a\nsimple transmitter in the case of the drone, and a transportable ground station\nin the case of the HAPS; and in the latter case the counter terminal is the GEO\nsatellite ETS-IX, foreseen to be launched by NICT in 2023.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 01:45:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
